item.title: Sweet Georgia Brown with Tractor on Kick
item.description: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=a1ThSi1wbqU Tractor repair and periodic availablity are two important services that SCD Hub collects and redistributes information on. This band has played alongside steam engines as well as a few kinds of these older farm tractors. They are not messing around either. Their playing is top shelf by any standard in the bluegrass music world.
